This is a quick script written for a presentation at Barcamp London 8

- Displays *.slide files in the directory where it is run
- Press left / A or right / D to navigate through slides
- Press Q to quit

For more info on ncurses and Python see:
http://docs.python.org/library/curses.html
http://davidbau.com/archives/2006/07/26/python_curses_life.html
